Topology base class

var topologyData = {
   nodes: [
       {"id": 0, "x": 410, "y": 100, "name": "12K-1"},
       {"id": 1, "x": 410, "y": 280, "name": "12K-2"},
       {"id": 2, "x": 660, "y": 280, "name": "Of-9k-03"},
       {"id": 3, "x": 660, "y": 100, "name": "Of-9k-02"},
       {"id": 4, "x": 180, "y": 190, "name": "Of-9k-01"}
   ],
   links: [
       {"source": 0, "target": 1},
       {"source": 1, "target": 2},
       {"source": 1, "target": 3},
       {"source": 4, "target": 1},
       {"source": 2, "target": 3},
       {"source": 2, "target": 0},
       {"source": 3, "target": 0},
       {"source": 3, "target": 0},
       {"source": 3, "target": 0},
       {"source": 0, "target": 4},
       {"source": 0, "target": 4},
       {"source": 0, "target": 3}
   ]
};
nx.define('MyTopology', nx.ui.Component, {
   view: {
       content: {
           type: 'nx.graphic.Topology',
           props: {
               width: 800,
               height: 800,
               nodeConfig: {
                   label: 'model.id'
               },
               showIcon: true,
               data: topologyData
           }
       }
   }
});
var app = new nx.ui.Application();
var comp = new MyTopology();
comp.attach(app);
